                        <h3 class="mdl-cell mdl-cell--12-col mdl-typography--headline">What I do here? </h3>
                        <div class="mdl-cell mdl-cell--6-col mdl-card__supporting-text no-padding">
                            <p>
                                My first project for the company was to work on the frontend of the admin panel for the company. The project
                                was using Angular.Js. I being the only frontend developer (in the beginning), was responsible for extending the 
                                features in the panel. This included from small features like making menus sticky on scroll, adding infinite scrolling,
                                adding lazy loading to images to big features such as creating full-fledged modules that are a product on their own. 
                                The backoffice project was created to allow customers, administrators and casino owners to manage all their websites, the content in it, 
                                the casino arcade terminal and clients who use our remote API. The scale of the project was massive and is still under heavy development. 
                                Due to the scale and the requirements we are currently porting the whole application to Angular 6. 
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mdl-cell mdl-cell--6-col">
