                                <img class="article-image hover-zoom shadow" src="/images/yellowportal.png" border="0" alt="automate deployment with webhooks">
                        </div>
                        <div class="mdl-cell mdl-cell--6-col mdl-card__supporting-text no-padding ">
                            <p>A few months into my job, our customers started requesting us to create custom casino websites that can be 
                                managed from our backoffice admin panel. These websites had very unique design requirements specific to the 
                                online gambling industry. The aim of these small projects were to create responsive, fast and secure pages. For this purpose,
                                we decided to use Angular 5 for these projects as these projects required maintainence and scalability options. Using techniques such as
                                lazy loading modules, split bundling, image sprites and server side rendering we were able to create quality casion web applications.</p>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="mdl-cell mdl-cell--12-col mdl-typography--headline"></h3>
