                        <div class="mdl-cell mdl-cell--8-col mdl-card__supporting-text no-padding ">
                            <p>
                                For the better part of the past month, I have started another project in the company. Its a CMS (Content management system),
                                that will aid our customers and us in creating dynamic websites themselves. So people who don't know anything about website
                                building will be able to to create their own custom websites. The end goal of this project is to create a universal applciation that can 
                                be used outside of the online gambling sector. However, since the project is young, I am keeping it simple and I am targetting casino websites
